pageContext.claim: “You know, the votes in Dominion, they say, are counted in foreign countries, OK? Can you believe this?”
pageContext.analysis: Utterly false. Trump is repeatedly a crazy claim made by his lawyer, former mayor Rudolph Giuliani. Votes in U.S. elections are not counted in foreign countries. “Votes are not processed outside the United States. Votes are counted and reported by county and state election officials — not by Dominion, or any other election technology company.” said Dominion Voting Systems in a statement.
